        "q_zh": "在边长为 5, 8, 10 的三角形中，求最大角最好使用哪个定理？",
        "o": [
          "Sine Rule",
          "Cosine Rule",
          "Pythagoras' Theorem",
          "SOH CAH TOA"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "When all three sides are known (SSS), the Cosine Rule is used to find angles.",
        "e_zh": "当已知三条边 (SSS) 时，使用余弦定理求角度。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "extended"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-6.5-03",
    "section": "6.5",
    "order": 3,
    "title": "Area of a Triangle",
    "title_zh": "三角形的面积",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "The **Area of a Triangle** can be calculated without knowing the height if you know two sides ($a$ and $b$) and the **included angle** ($C$).\n\nFormula: $\\text{Area} = \\frac{1}{2}ab \\sin C$\n\nThis formula is useful for non-right-angled triangles where the vertical height is not easily found.",
      "zh": "如果已知三角形的两条边（$a$ 和 $b$）及其**夹角**（$C$），可以在不知道高的情况下计算**三角形的面积**。\n\n公式：$\\text{面积} = \\frac{1}{2}ab \\sin C$\n\n该公式对于难以求得垂高的非直角三角形非常有用。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-area-trig",
        "label": "Calculate triangle area using sine",
        "label_zh": "利用正弦计算三角形面积",
        "description": "Find the area of a triangle given SAS (Side-Angle-Side).",
        "description_zh": "已知两边及其夹角，求三角形面积。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-area-trig",
        "question": "Find the area of a triangle with sides 6 cm and 9 cm and an included angle of $35^\\circ$.",
